  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.173290664265942         -4.7155          -108.74          -454.97
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.053277737607281          1.4498            33.43           139.88
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.029311955056693         -0.7976           -18.39           -76.96
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.117884112806563          3.2078            73.97           309.50
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

